                        About Us
                    


Ideal Power has invented, patented and commercialized a revolutionary new technology that significantly improves the weight, size, cost, efficiency and reliability of electronic power converters - the conduits to modern energy. Based on patented Power Packet Switching Architecture (PPSA) that uses a standard lightweight hardware design and embedded application-specific software, Ideal Power serves the multi-billion dollar power conversion markets of renewable energy, electrical energy efficiency, smart grids and electric vehicles. Ideal Power products include solar inverters, bi-directional battery and electric vehicle chargers, all built on the same lightweight Universal Power Converter Platform.





                        Why Us
                    


Transformative Innovation in the Power Conversion IndustryBy harnessing the power of software and semiconductor technology, we have developed a power conversion system technology that uses transformerless isolation, eliminating the bulky and inefficient components that have been the mainstay of power conversion for decades. This new approach results in power conversion systems that are smaller, lighter, more reliable and more efficient than conventional technologies, dramatically reducing installed costs.Next Generation Technology for the Clean Energy EconomyIn addition to the ongoing development of our current products, we have received patents for a new bidirectional silicon power switch design, the B-TRAN, which will further improve our competitive advantage in weight, size, cost reductions and efficiency.Powered by Creative ThinkingIdeal Power has been granted more than 40 patents in the U.S., Europe, China and other countries around the globe, with additional patents pending. We continue to aggressively pursue intellectual property protection for our current and future technologies to maintain our leadership position in the industry.





                        Applications
                    


Energy StorageEnabling Technology to Cap Peak DemandBecause our products pair well with all leading battery technologies, they optimize the performance of battery storage and provide the best value on the market for peak demand management applications.Maximizing the value of energy storage means stripping away unnecessary components and processes that waste power. With considerable size and weight advantages, our systems have lower shipping and installation costs compared to conventional technology. Our power conversion systems are unobtrusive with a compact footprint and near silent operation, making them the ideal choice for EPCs, developers and energy storage system integrators.Renewable IntegrationA Key Component of the Clean Energy InfrastructureAs society’s energy demand begins to outpace utilities’ peak generation capacity, there is an increasing need to incorporate new forms of renewable energy into the grid. Our grid resilient, multi-port technology is the most efficient way to enable the convergence of renewable and conventional energy to support growing energy demand.Microgrids & Critical PowerContributing to Global Energy Security and IndependenceOur grid resilient technology integrates solar PV and conventional generation with battery storage to deliver stable, flexible and reliable energy whether on-grid or off-grid. Compatible with both 50Hz and 60Hz environments, our systems enable energy applications from microgrids to grid support in a variety of global markets.






