STABLE, FLEXIBLE

CLEAN ENERGY

and RELIABLE








  ENERGY STORAGE
Enabling Technology to Cap Peak Demand
Because our products pair well with all leading battery technologies, they optimize the performance of battery storage and provide the best value on the market for peak demand management applications.
Maximizing the value of energy storage means stripping away unnecessary components and processes that waste power. With considerable size and weight advantages, our systems have lower shipping and installation costs compared to conventional technology. Our power conversion systems are unobtrusive with a compact footprint and near silent operation, making them the ideal choice for EPCs, developers and energy storage system integrators.

  RENEWABLE INTEGRATION
A Key Component of the Clean Energy Infrastructure
As society’s energy demand begins to outpace utilities’ peak generation capacity, there is an increasing need to incorporate new forms of renewable energy into the grid. Our grid resilient, multi-port technology is the most efficient way to enable the convergence of renewable and conventional energy to support growing energy demand.
 

  MICROGRIDS & CRITICAL POWER
Contributing to Global Energy Security and Independence
Our grid resilient technology integrates solar PV and conventional generation with battery storage to deliver stable, flexible and reliable energy whether on-grid or off-grid. Compatible with both 50Hz and 60Hz environments, our systems enable energy applications from microgrids to grid support in a variety of global markets.
