The Catalyst of Innovation is in our Core
By harnessing the power of software and semiconductor technology, Ideal Power has developed our patented Power Packet Switching Architecture (PPSA™) eliminating the bulky and inefficient passive components that have been the mainstay of power conversion for decades. This new approach results in power conversion systems that are smaller, lighter, more reliable and more efficient than conventional technologies, dramatically reducing installation costs while increasing return on investment.
 
 PPSA Whitepaper
Enabling Renewable Energy Revolution
The success of solar-plus-storage – which has gained recent traction and is expected to continue to grow – depends largely on effective inverter technologies as well. Solar-plus-storage in the commercial sector has the ability to reduce demand charge risk, minimize costs and enhance the resilience of a building’s power supply.
Because our products pair well with leading battery technologies, they optimize the performance of energy storage and provide the best value on the market for peak demand management, alternating current (AC) microgrids, direct current (DC) microgrids and backup power applications.
Our grid-resilient, bidirectional multiport technology is the most effective way to enable the convergence of renewable and conventional energy. Our technologies support variable energy demand, enabling energy from any port, to any port, as well as on or off the grid.
Product Line
30 kW Stabiliti™ Series Multiport Power Conversion SystemOrdering Model No. 30C3
The Stabiliti™ Series PCS is galvanically isolated, indoor/outdoor rated, and is the smallest PCS in its class.  The 30C3 model is a multiport hybrid power converter supporting bi-directional power flows between all three of its power ports (AC-DC-DC) enabling a variety of applications such as solar+storage, demand management, EV charging, backup power and microgrids.
 Documentation for Model No. 30C3 


 Data Sheet
 Certificate of Compliance
 Limited Warranty North America




 Limited Warranty International
 Quick Start Guide
 I & O Manual




 App Notes




30 kW Stabiliti™ Series Dual Port Power Conversion SystemOrdering Model No. 30C
The Stabiliti™ Series PCS is galvanically isolated, indoor/outdoor rated, and is the smallest PCS in its class. This Series is also stackable so multiple units can work together to support higher power applications at 60 kW, 90 kW and more.  The 30C model is a power converter supports bi-directional power flows between both of its power ports (AC-DC) enabling storage applications such as demand management, EV charging, backup power resiliency, and microgrids.
 Documentation for Model No. 30C 


 Data Sheet
 Certificate of Compliance
 Limited Warranty North America




 Limited Warranty International
 Quick Start Guide
 I & O Manual




 App Notes




30 kW SunDial™ and SuDial™ Plus SeriesGrid-tied Commercial PV String InverterOrdering Model Numbers: 30PV, 30PVF, 30PV+S, 30PVF+S
The SunDial™ 30PV is a 30kW PV String Inverter with an integrated 6-String PV Combiner, and DC Disconnect.   The SunDial™ Plus model features a factory installed, low cost plug-and-play, bi-directional DC port (models 30PV+S, 30PVF+S) for commercial solar + storage applications.  Both versions include a newly redesigned PPSA™ AC Link delivering true galvanic isolation between the AC and DC ports.   This isolation provides superior battery fault protection and enables PV installations to be either grounded-referenced (models 30PV, 30PV+S) or floating (models 30PVF, 30PVF+S).
 Documentation for Model Numbers: 30PV, 30PVF, 30PV+S, 30PVF+S 


 Data Sheet
